Package: FastTail
Title: An R package for Fast Inference on Bivariate Tail Dependence and Tail Asymmetry Using Neural Bayes Estimators
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Lei", "Hua", email = "larry.lei.hua@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast inference of various tail dependence and tail asymmetry patterns for bivariate copulas. 
	It for now covers the GGEE and the PPPP copulas.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
	JuliaConnectoR (== 1.1.4),
	NeuralEstimators (== 0.2.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
